        "URI": "-",
        "DOI": "https://doi.org/10.2134/agronj1994.00021962008600060014x",
        "Extended description": "Computes soil temperature by layer. STEMP orchestrates initialization, daily rate updates and output control, and calls SOILT to compute layer temperatures using damping depth (Parton & Logan) method; includes surface temperature for CENTURY-based SOM/soil-N module.",
        "Short description": "Determines soil temperature by layer",
        "Model version": "1.0"
    },
